title: War of the Roses: The Headprint In the Pillow
description: Kendall calls us to find out if her boyfriend Joey is cheating on her because he sent her a selfie the other day and she noticed a headprint in the pillow on the side he never sleeps on.  Did he just switch it up or was someone else in his bed?
